title: Reward Claimed: GTA$250,000
headline: Reward Claimed: GTA$250,000
subtitle: You Reached LS Car Meet Reputation Level 20
content:
Your GTA$250,000 bonus Reward for reaching LS Car Meet reputation level 20 between July 20 and August 18 has been deposited into your Maze Bank Account.

Stay tuned to the Rockstar Newswire for more limited-time events coming soon to Los Santos.
